divs: Sighting DetailsIn a 33 min. time span I witnessed 2 seperate lights that appeared to look like stars and third that my wife got to witness.There were planes and jets flying around and were all very distinct execpt for these star like objects that seemed to be flying a greater speed than jets and planes.The first 2 objects came into sight at different times in different locations both traveling west to east.The 3rd object witnessed by my wife and I was traveling south to north, first coming into sight in the same vacinity as the first 2.
